title: Grateful Dead Live at Nassau Coliseum on 1993-04-05
description:
Set 1

Touch Of Grey, Greatest Story Ever Told, Lazy River Road, Just Like Tom Thumb's Blues, Black Throated Wind, Tennessee Jed, The Music Never Stopped, Deal

Set 2

I Fought The Law, Way To Go Home, Corinna-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Jam-> I Need A Miracle-> Wharf Rat-> Gloria, E: U.S. Blues
